name: .SHSH2 File Extension
summary: Learn about .SHSH2 files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: SHSH2 files are not meant to be opened. Those looking to downgrade to a previous version of iOS can use jailbreaking tools such as iFaith (Windows), 3uTools (Windows), and futurerestore (cross-platform) to use an SHSH2 file to install a previous version of iOS.
